This experience was created for the Inspire 2025 Challenge. Submission for the ROBLOX Inspire 2024 Challenge (https://devforum.roblox.com/t/roblox-inspire-2024-challenge/3104238).

SUMMARY:
Your character (Mort, the mushroom) is fighting for his life against a time-controlling deity known as "Abuelo." If Mort wins, he is no longer subject to the effects of passing time and can live forever in peace.

The remaining timer is your health, if it hits zero, you lose. Parrying restores some timer so you can keep the fight going.

There are four phases, each one introducing a new mechanic:
1: Simple hand attacks
2: Spinning clock face on the stage
3: Falling objects
4: Max timer of 1:00

Beating the game awards you with a badge for your efforts! Good luck everyone.

gameData.title: The Nuclear Paradox
gameData.description:
You are a scientist who is attempting to stop a nuclear apocalypse from happening. In a last-ditch effort, you use an experimental backpack that lets you travel back in time, but only for a short period. Your mission is to go back in time and prevent the events that lead to the apocalypse. To do this, you must journey into the past. The backpack's power is limited, so you'll need to recharge it by finding energy sources scattered throughout the past. If you run out of power, time will start reversing, sending you back to the present and erasing all your progress. Every mistake brings the apocalypse closer. Can you beat the clock, change the past, and save the world? Or will time become your enemy?

gameData.title: The Adventures of Mr. Newton

"The Adventures of Mr. Newton" invites players to immerse themselves in the thrilling life of a young detective, Mr. Newton, navigating a city steeped in mysteries and criminal intrigue. As the sun sets, Detective Newton stumbles upon a series of complex cases, each requiring players to utilize deductive reasoning and keen investigative skills.

Set in a dynamic cityscape, the game offers a diverse range of environments for players to explore, from shadowy alleyways to opulent mansions. Armed with a trusty magnifying glass, players must interrogate witnesses, examine crime scenes, and solve puzzles to unravel the interconnected web of mysteries.

The gameplay combines puzzle-solving, exploration, and deduction, creating an engaging experience that keeps players on the edge of their seats. Along the way, players encounter a colorful cast of characters, each with their own motives and secrets, adding depth to the narrative.

Will you be able to crack the case? Join now and find out!
